Existing reservations for upcoming travel between March 14 and April 30, 2020:
All existing reservations made before March 13, 2020 that are for arrivals between March 14 and April 30, 2020 can be changed or cancelled at no charge up to 24 hours before your scheduled arrival. This includes Advance Purchase Rate reservations
.•
New reservations for any future travel:
It is our desire to accommodate your travel plans with as much flexibility as you need to book with confidence. Many of our rate offerings have been tailored to meet the needs of today’s travelers with flexible change and cancellation policies, however, if you are unable to find a plan that meets your need please reach out the us directly as we have many options to amend your travel plans as necessary.
•
Existing Advance Purchase Rate non-refundable reservations for travel through June 2020:
As announced earlier, special exceptions are in place for all Advance Purchase Rate non-refundable reservations made directly with Guy Harvey Resort St. Augustine Beach on or before March 8, 2020 for arrivals before June 30, 2020.
For full details and to make arrangements, please contact us directly at (904) 471-2555 or email us at
[email protected]
.Guests who booked via online travel agents or other third parties are advised to contact their booking provider for information on their policies and for assistance.
On behalf of the entire Guy Harvey Resort St. Augustine Beach family, we would like to reiterate that the safety and wellbeing of our guests and associates, remain our highest priority.
